      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT DOMINO (1) won by 6 lengths last start when getting around this track 400m in a convincing 22.63. Hard to top on the time from last start. MY NAMES ROCKY (2) was an impressive winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 2 length second at this track (22.82). Got the money at his only try from this box. Can measure up. DUNDEE REX (4) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 4.5 lengths second last start at Bendigo over 425m (24.56). Expected to be in this for a long way.",
